claim.claim-text:
7. A reticle handling arm apparatus for handling a reticle, comprising: 
a base portion; 
two spaced apart support arms extending outwardly from the base portion for engaging a lower surface of the reticle; 
one or more reticle stop blocks fixed relative to the handling arm and positioned to engage an edge of the reticle so as to assure accurate placement of the reticle in a desired position on the support arms.
